    "It is commonly held that Large Language Models (LLMs) [9,16,54,67] will have a far-reaching impact and be employed as aides by numerous professionals.",
    "This encompasses, among others, solving mathematical questions in an exam format and examining ChatGPT's behavior in various mathematical situations.",
    "ChatGPT is trained on a large corpus of text and is capable of generating new text based on the patterns it has learned from the training data.",
    "Responses in various domains can be so convincing that it becomes difficult to distinguish if they were written by a human or not.",
    "It can write sophisticated essays and poems, create functional code, and build charts and websites from text descriptions with little to no guidance."
